{"id": 1050, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都有过哪些大脑当机的时刻？", "description": "脑子仿佛突然被拔了电源，瞬间智障。(题图来自：Lobke van Aar)", "record_count": 5943, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703152314mNI2TuVBQiJ8gFpj.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-06-09T01:00:03Z", "options": [{"id": 86528, "content": "主题是什么来着，让我再粗去看一下", "image": null, "praise_count": 50, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 594914}, {"id": 86784, "content": "公寓式的大学宿舍住在405却频频走进305", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 634720}, {"id": 87040, "content": "被闹钟吵醒的一瞬间。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 636072}, {"id": 86529, "content": "晚上摘完隐形眼镜，无意识的按照刚戴完眼镜的程序，把眼镜盒里的水直接甩干，还擦了擦。第二天找不到眼镜，在地上找到了眼镜的尸体……", "image": null, "praise_count": 40, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 613988}, {"id": 86785, "content": "小便你写错字了吧，是宕机不是当机", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 270432}, {"id": 88065, "content": "突然所有密码都忘记了....", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 643762}, {"id": 86530, "content": "我刚才想说啥来着？", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 125521}, {"id": 86786, "content": "看见熟人上去打招呼，突然就想不起来对方的姓名～", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 597069}, {"id": 88834, "content": "打开手机 看着这些APP 诶 我要点哪个嘞？我要干嘛呢。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1219928}, {"id": 86787, "content": "当着所有人的面演讲的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 640045}, {"id": 87043, "content": "走进一个房间后忘了为什么要进来", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 493466}, {"id": 86532, "content": "每次输入密码的时候，我都符合以上条件…", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 287241}, {"id": 86788, "content": "一戴框镜出门就懵逼～", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 624708}, {"id": 90628, "content": "无意识地把面前的饮料一瓶瓶打开", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 650805}, {"id": 86533, "content": "突然忘记别人名字", "image": null, "praise_count": 546, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 419840}, {"id": 89605, "content": "我要做什么来着？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 648568}, {"id": 86790, "content": "突然忘了自己想干什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 579533}, {"id": 86535, "content": "高考数学考完出门想起填空题没往答题卡上抄", "image": null, "praise_count": 59, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 639503}, {"id": 86791, "content": "永远不记得银行卡密码", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 579533}, {"id": 86536, "content": "忘记密码比如银行卡密码", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 636563}, {"id": 86792, "content": "要用的东西就在手上还在满房间找", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 469244}, {"id": 86793, "content": "想做一件事情，一转身忘了。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 636777}, {"id": 86538, "content": "我进来干什么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 93, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 219212}, {"id": 86794, "content": "诶 我要评论什么来着", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 533889}, {"id": 87050, "content": "在食堂打包饭菜，打包好拿了就走，忘了筷子……关键在回的路上差不多十分钟都没想起来……", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 639306}, {"id": 86539, "content": "知道前任有对象", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 639506}, {"id": 86795, "content": "有一天晚上网吧通宵~我突然眼前一黑感觉就是来不及思考发生了什么失去意识，然后我醒来的时候朋友说我没几秒~当时真的感觉就是机器人失去电力这样子。。。可能血糖低吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 600138}, {"id": 87051, "content": "累的半死的时候。说话不经过大脑", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 633591}, {"id": 86540, "content": "哎？！我妈叫什么来着！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 629344}, {"id": 86796, "content": "发现自己手机掉了 ，到处找原来在手上", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 640059}, {"id": 86541, "content": "拿着两样一摸一样的东西 一样新的一样旧的  想把旧的扔了 结果...", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 636720}, {"id": 86797, "content": "我到这里要干什么来着？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 618498}, {"id": 86542, "content": "打电话发现拿的是遥控，咋没声，出声啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 619207}, {"id": 87054, "content": "走上从楼下下来的电梯，等着被送到楼上，两次", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 635827}, {"id": 86543, "content": "三次走进505寝室的时候！然而我住605！", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 639513}, {"id": 86799, "content": "开着导航也找不到路", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147506}, {"id": 86544, "content": "早上起来跟室友说我做了一个超级吊的梦。室友问什么梦？    答：我忘了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 222, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 78499}, {"id": 86800, "content": "我眼镜呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 640060}, {"id": 87056, "content": "答辩的时候突然放空，剩下在场专家们在苦等", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 640792}, {"id": 86545, "content": "无时无刻不在找东西?", "image": null, "praise_count": 40, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 78499}, {"id": 86801, "content": "不知道要干什么了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 635658}, {"id": 87057, "content": "有人向我表白的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 609712}, {"id": 86802, "content": "排队啊  排队啊。无限期", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 635658}, {"id": 87058, "content": "背课文的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 627865}, {"id": 86547, "content": "手里拿着手机还在找手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 85, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 172466}, {"id": 86803, "content": "上厕所出来准备睡了 忘记自己有没有冲厕所！又回去看了一次发现冲了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 638237}, {"id": 86548, "content": "出门走了一段路 开始怀疑自己有没有关门！", "image": null, "praise_count": 395, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 632270}, {"id": 86804, "content": "我刚刚想要说什么来着？", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 255265}, {"id": 86549, "content": "写稿的时候需要配图，很着急地拿起手机找图，解锁之后忘记我拿手机干嘛", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 639520}, {"id": 86805, "content": "想要跟人阐述意见的时候，用手机打字往往很顺畅。见了面之后经常会有“诶？我刚才想说什么来着？”这样的状况。 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 620514}]}